title: Simple Note Taking App
about: A simple note taking app. It is a front end app that allows users to add notes, delete notes. It also time stamps when the note is created.

title: Vanilla JS Calculator
about: A Vanilla JS project that is modelled on the mac default calculator. It allows users to do all the basic operations. It allows users to continuously add, subtract, divide or multiply.

title: Mock FAQ Accordian
about: A simple FAQ page for an imaginery company. Based on a Frontend Mentor challenge. It uses flexbox to help it make it responsive
